quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, huliree Joomi mon …óoftagol ko O yamiri on kon, e nantagol ko O ha…ói on kon e mu'un, anndo, ko wondata kon e Darngal ngal immorde dillugol leydi ndin e tanaa mu'un e kulaleeji …óin, …óum ko fiyaake maw…óo, no wa…ó…óii heblanorgol …óum gollugol ko weltinta Alla."
  22,2,"√ëalnde seedoyto…óon kala muyninaykun no welsindoo e ko kun muyninaynoo kon, kala sowiikun jibina ko kun sowinoo kon immorde e sa…ótude kulol ngol, a yi'ay yim…ìe …ìen sabu wirnagol hakkillaaji ma…ì…ìe hi…ìe wa'i wa siwru…ìe immorde e sa…ótude kulol Darorde nden, …ìe wonaa siwrir…ìe yarugol beere, kono Lepte Alla …óen ko sattu…óe, …óe waasinii …ìe hakkillaaji ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  22,3,"No e yim…ìe …ìen on wennjoowo e fii Bawngal Alla e dow immintingol may…ìe …ìen ko aldaa e ganndal ngal o tuugii e mu'un, o jokka e finnde makko nden e konngol makko ngol kala sanndal…óii…óo e dow Joomi mu'un immorde e Seytanuuji …óin, e yeesoo…ìe majjere nden."
  22,4,"Winndaama e dow on sanndal…óii…óo immorde e Seytanuuji yim…ìe e jinna wonnde kala jokku…óo mo o goongini mo haray kanko o majjinay mo gaayi Laawol Goongawol ngol, o sogga mo haaa ka Lepte yiite ngen sabu ko o …óowata mo kon e muu…óum immorde e keefeeru ngun e geddi …óin."
  22,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, si tawii sikke no ka mo'on fii Kattan…óe Amen e dow immintinngol on …ìaawo mayde nden, awa taskee e tagu mo'on ngun; gom…óii Men Tagiino baaba moo…óon Aadama e mbulaare, refti Men Tagi …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen immorde e maniiyo mo gorko on werlotoo …óum e nder rannga suddii…óo on, refti maniyo on wonta ∆¥ii∆¥am fenndii…óam, refti ∆¥ii∆¥am fenndii…óam …óam wonta huyre teewu nanndunde e huyre ∆¥akkaande refti huyre nden wonta tagu timmungu ngu heddoo ka rennga haa jibinaa…óo wuuru…óo yalta, maa…óum le tagu ngu timmaa rennga on fukka …óum; fii yo Men …ìannginan on Kattan…óe Amen e Tagugol on e alhaaliiji, Men tabintina ka renngaaji ko Men Muuyi kon immorde e cawli haa …ói jibinee e dummunne happaa…óo …óum ko lebbi jeenay, refti Men yaltina on ka deedi neeniraa…ìe mo'on ko on booboo…ìe, refti fii yo on yotto faade e timmal doole e hakkil, no e mo'on on mo no maaya ado …óum, no e mo'on kadi on mo no wuura haa o yottoo duu…ìi nayewu nokku ka doole …óen e hakkille …óen lo'ata, haa o wonta …ìur…óo bonude alhaali diini boobo on, hara o annditataa hay e huunde ko o anndunoo kon, a yi'ay leydi ndin ko yoorundi pu…ói alaa e mayri, si Men jippinii e mayri to…ìo ngon ndi udditanoo pu…ói …óin, ndi ∆¥ura sabu …ìeydagol pu…ói mayri, ndi yaltina kala noone immorde e pu…ói labaa…ói ndarngo."